node.text: Hey everyone. To welcome all of you to CU Blueprint we made an introduction video introducing our members, activities, and what we're all about. Make sure to grab your popcorn and give it a watch! 😄
a part of our team finally got to meet each other irl! 🍣🦐🧑‍🔧💙

node.text:
Allo Canada Team Showcase // Part 3

Aaaand that’s a wrap 🎬 on our 3rd project!! 🙌🏽🏆

For the past 8 months, the Allo Canada team has partnered with the Refugee Center on a collaborative mission to create a new and accessible integration journey dashboard for immigrants and refugees settling in Canada 🇨🇦

This team put so much dedication, talent and effort into the success of this project 🚀 and we wanted to show the world who our amazing members are 🔥

node.text:
📢It's that time of the year again! CU Blueprint is recruiting for the 2023-24 year!

With available roles on our Work Place Stop Project and Executive team, now's your chance to make a difference and showcase your skills! 

Click the link in our bio, click "Join Blueprint" and apply to be a part of CU Blueprint! 🚀

⁉️Questions or concerns, DM us!

node.text:
Have no idea what to expect for the upcoming job hunt? Scared about applying to your first (or even your last) internship? Blueprint's got your back! 

Join us November 30th (online) at 6PM to hear about our very own blueprint members' experience with the internship season! 💼 

Make sure to sign up using our QR code or the link in bio to get the zoom link!
